----

Download page: https://buster.me.uk/

See the uniform polyhedra! See them morph! See them spin! See them bounce!

Instructions: Right-click on the ".scr" file and choose "Test", "Configure" or "Install".
See the file "INSTALL" for instructions on how to build the screensaver from source.
